    "composition_of_independent_variables": "The independent variables were the type of polymer coating (Surelease, Ethyl cellulose N50, Kollicoat SR 30D) and the percentage of coating (7.5%, 10%, 12.5%, 15%) for pellets. For tablets, the independent variable was the concentration of Lubritab (0, 10, 15, 20 mg/tablet).",
    "ftir_spectral_measurements": {
        "method": "About 2 mg of sample was mixed with dried KBr, pressed into a pellet, and scanned from 4000 to 400 cm-1 in a spectrophotometer.",
        "findings": "FT-IR spectra showed typical peaks for Metoprolol succinate, confirming its purity. No significant interactions or instability were observed between the drug and excipients (Ethyl cellulose N50, Kollicoat SR30D). Major peaks for functional groups (C-N, C-H Alkane, N-H Bending, OCH3-stretching, C=C) showed no significant change in physical mixtures.",
